<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Jun1924"><font color="red">8 June 1924</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Having nothing to do or read or write I am waiting for the next two days to pass. I have taken a flat in Nice &hellip; from 1 October to 1 May </div>
